des:
Learn about Catholicism via eye-catching videos produced by Catholic Telemedia Network. Simply say - Alexa, ask 'Roman Catholic' to play a video. Or, you can search for a video matching your interest. For example: You can say - Alexa, ask 'Roman Catholic' to play a video on 'baptism'. We will slowly add more videos to the existing ones to cover the entire spectrum of helpful resources in Catholic faith. Stay tuned. Amen.

Learn more at https://www.catholicteacherresources.com
